Subject:    <a href="?t=95837890700017&r=1&w=2">Re: root server problems?</a>
From:       <a href="?a=95837785800033&r=1&w=2">aramis.rutgers.edu!geneva.rutgers.edu!hedrick () rutgers ! edu  (Charles Hedrick)</a>
